METEOR idea

Meteor pinball spinner rules

lvl 1
    each drop down adds X points
    spinner rips = base * drops down
    complete 3 or 6 drops resets drops
        add to base value for complete?

lvl 2
    drops down add X points
        drops position (fixed) adds X points
        ie M and R are worth more
        
lvl 3
    most valuable drop moving side to side
        lock in high value or low value
        
lvl 4
    most valuable and 0 value moving side to side
    
lvl 5
    only lit adds value to spinner rip
